---
title: Cheesy Mexican Style Beef Hash with Crispy Potato Top and Guacamole
description: This Cheesy Mexican Style Beef Hash is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-mexican-style-beef-hash-1552ad4b-f7e6d92e.jpg
